==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Zoned
<hw>Zoned</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Wearing a
zone, or girdle.</def> <rj><au>Pope.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Having zones, or concentric bands;
striped.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Zonate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Zoneless</ent>⟦br⟧
